{"tid":500641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［早早變左劏遊客啦］墾丁旅客恐跌破500萬　 比三年前減六成","createTime":"2017-12-16T03:42:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-16T13:10:38.000Z","uid":110876,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"2387b37c283908eaf6350ab8015c4f3d0047bd17","tid":500641,"uid":110876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:42:06.000Z","msg":"墾丁有「國境之南」美譽，亦深受港人熱愛，但近年墾丁的旅客人數斷崖式直插，估計今年屏東墾丁國家公園旅客人數將跌破500萬人次，與3年前相比跌幅高達約6成。台觀光局認為與大陸旅客減少有關，不過不少網民認為墾丁消費貴及業界營商不實趕走旅客。<br />\n<br />\n墾丁國家公園管理處統計，3年前該處仍有800萬旅客，但去年開始暴跌，當地今年1月至10月，旅客總數約344萬，比去年同期的484萬，減少了140萬人。去年當地旅客整年合共546萬，因此估計今年當地旅客將不足500萬人。<br />\n台觀光局副局長張錫聰解釋，墾丁上半年受大陸旅客減少影響，但下半年和去年人數相若。他認為新旅客先到台北及台中，重遊旅客才會到台南，故未來會加強向新旅客宣傳墾丁。他又透露，政府會與墾丁聯手，推出農業博覽會及運動觀光，又將墾丁落山風包裝成旅遊區，宣傳墾丁豐年祭。<br />\n網民對於墾丁旅客大減嗤之以鼻，認為問題不在宣傳，而是當地消費貴，業界營商不實。台網絡紅人兼律師呂秋遠曾分析，若在墾丁5日4夜自由行，當地五星級酒店一晚索價1.2萬（約3,100港元），單是住宿就4.8萬（1.25萬港元），4天租車連高鐵，交通費要3萬（約7,800元），住宿交通合共9萬元（2.3萬港元），他指出這個價錢已經可以去日本京都及沖繩。<br />\n<br />\n滷味太貴惹非議<br />\n<br />\n近日墾丁大街商戶再次爆出醜聞，有旅客在13日於當地「吳師傅滷味」叫了一盤滷味，竟然索價920台幣（下同，約239港元），認為貴也算了，但「味道及新鮮度，實在令人無法接受」。他在自己社交網站抱怨，結果竟傳遍全台，不少人認為個案正是墾丁旅客大減的主因。該店主昨天回應指，根據該旅客的點的菜式，售價應只是約660元（約172港元）。該旅客之後上載收據，證明自己無含血噴人。<br />\n有網友扮日本人到該店用日語買滷味，他叫了像番茄般大小的青椒、粗約尾指的豬耳、乒乓球大小的豬腱、鹽酥雞大小的芋簽粿，該店索價205元（約53港元），令網民再起爭議，直斥：「請問是有灑金箔嗎，還是墾丁是在第三次元世界？」<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》/《自由時報》"},{"pid":"24917367dedf201b976ccd8c2c02ce9ea14d079a","tid":500641,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:48:59.000Z","msg":"3萬交通，俾人當儍仔？"},{"pid":"078038a87c7f2cac960e4926666ab9060c827d0f","tid":500641,"uid":41116,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:51:04.000Z","msg":"台灣最美的風景是人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d405c0e655446b6a282129cbe1bd2adbdbd34d3","tid":500641,"uid":25838,"like":13,"dislike":16,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"垃圾台灣<br />\n早就比垃圾中國低等"},{"pid":"28b20b7cc8ae3137db3fed3a4378f7891f64e0ba","tid":500641,"uid":76681,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"成日吹奏台灣人最好既去左邊?"},{"pid":"2146e98f93935173c3f662e3ae9e1753a38ce521","tid":500641,"uid":113626,"like":2,"dislike":20,"score":-18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"點解仲有人去亞洲呢d垃圾區<br />\n唔去美國歐洲都唔好話自已去旅行 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c01af47322ce8d7ef001f9fc391b71120671eb","tid":500641,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T04:39:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65501e0ce8827859f0c18b88cae463c2a04de83","tid":500641,"uid":81756,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:00:01.000Z","msg":"支那外島<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b8b0fd4efb00127e2b6aaa9463191f147aa452c","tid":500641,"uid":1166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:03:09.000Z","msg":"墾丁入面d 人全部生藩咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b40e5e88d45bb3859f6aa7f003fa1a3d7d193b4","tid":500641,"uid":3112,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:13:39.000Z","msg":"正常發揮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n人情味？你有錢比咪有人情味囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n住耐d根本就會知同支那一鳩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n狗改不了吃屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62ff24cdb4757dbf1aba889786d5d8be356426a","tid":500641,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ae76631af3f2c11bf0898dcc43b601ca4e39d51","tid":500641,"uid":21222,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:19:56.000Z","msg":"4-5年前去過一次，一般遊客價錢又未話好貴既。仲有得唔洗牌揸電單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好爽風景空氣又好，返香港即刻考牌買車點知兩回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24485b90cbd094738bac8e4f67171093389cbd3d","tid":500641,"uid":38666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:27:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾台灣<br />\n早就比垃圾中國低等</blockquote><br />\n竟然低等過支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"756c6a4c0b32df8610db85d476f59dc5c9417a4b","tid":500641,"uid":24526,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:52:46.000Z","msg":"7年前去住間民宿<br />\n原本book咗三晚房<br />\n但一到步就颱風 大風大雨邊到都無得去<br />\n決定第二日提早出高雄 <br />\n提早退房都預咗無錢退<br />\n點知還鎖匙嗰陣個老闆娘塞返兩日房錢比我地<br />\n仲叫我地下次好天再黎墾丁 好好玩咁話<br />\n但之後都無再去過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7de0b32f859cd278e877473f0442c8c765d2b873","tid":500641,"uid":25086,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:54:39.000Z","msg":"咪老作新聞啦<br />\n台灣最美的風景是人<br />\n係咪寫記中國啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca22c8a4729cc647fdd8d92cd55ad55d77d8f59d","tid":500641,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:54:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪老作新聞啦<br />\n台灣最美的風景是人<br />\n係咪寫錯中國啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"685a71f3fd492cc37bc082e4ff8fd7c44c57e0f4","tid":500641,"uid":25086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7年前去住間民宿<br />\n原本book咗三晚房<br />\n但一到步就颱風 大風大雨邊到都無得去<br />\n決定第二日提早出高雄 <br />\n提早退房都預咗無錢退<br />\n點知還鎖匙嗰陣個老闆娘塞返兩日房錢比我地<br />\n仲叫我地下次好天再黎墾丁 好好玩咁話<br />\n但之後都無再去過了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502c47c6ad9a06bb5a31105c3903e74310cdba91","tid":500641,"uid":52595,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:03:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2cbc8ff40bbde8d7f6e079a2d1684d030290507a","tid":500641,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd3234707fbef82d1bbcaaf404c71d7f76cd0e34","tid":500641,"uid":7332,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:08:52.000Z","msg":"去撚過幾次 班台灣朋友都屌墾丁愈來愈廢。<br />\n搵hostel住難，就算有都好廢，上次去到，個廁所臭既，想轉住民宿，貴撚到嚇死人。<br />\n條大街廢既，一堆呃鳩人既攤位遊戲，賣既野食味精重撚到。<br />\n最垃圾既係海灘，真係唔明點解咁出名，又嘈又多垃圾。<br />\n跟住又有一堆想呃鳩人錢既的士"},{"pid":"3ca32926abb211a5bb2dfe54a42cc35bc0f857e5","tid":500641,"uid":7332,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:09:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未搭過飛機未去過外地旅遊先會比上面班友呃到！<br />\n<br />\n人地點對你，睇下你有無禮貌啦！<br />\n一家幾口嘈喧巴弊，去到邊都人見人僧啦！</blockquote><br />\n你錯了。班所謂小店既店主真係串過馬撚"},{"pid":"f13fe5e47e3188b6e0b1aaec06fc4300db20e2db","tid":500641,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:13:21.000Z","msg":"講緊劏人又講禮貌<br />\n有禮貌著唔劏你？"},{"pid":"be2c68ebf24f5d5a6faa5d896db8848d365ddbe9","tid":500641,"uid":41818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:15:22.000Z","msg":"台灣去過一次就夠 垃圾地方<br />\n去日本唔撚好？"},{"pid":"b019d2856b823decd6697763999568bc6f90f1cb","tid":500641,"uid":10453,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"無乜大陸人嗰陣去過<br />\n<br />\n有一日踩單車環墾丁，去到中後段斷水斷糧，見到間飄沙舖，想同佢哋買枝水，佢見我哋係遊客又敢環墾丁咁癲（原來全上山路，唔怪之得咁難踩），二話不說送咗枝幾L水俾我哋，仲唔肯收錢<br />\n<br />\n都係環丁中途，今次去到個沙灘，個沙灘因為就打風封咗，有對外國人唔知(得中文告示），個救生員又唔識英文，我哋就埋去幫手。之後救生員送咗兩條台灣糉俾我哋食，同埋吹吓水咁。<br />\n<br />\n其實墾丁幾好玩，不過無咩再去一次嘅衝動就真嘅，加上後期咁多大陸人去，更加唔會想去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/27.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a17f4679fc60a5d33ac5f99b3d8d9cc221face88","tid":500641,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-16T06:19:42.000Z","msg":"墾丁野食唔多掂 日日都去恆春開飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}